{"lemma":"حَبْلَيْ","slug":"حَبْلَيْ","root":"ح.ب.ل","root_slug":"ح-ب-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ب-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَبْل","root":"حبل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":4,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":7},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6974","n6975"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a rope, a cable; a hawser; a cord; a string; a thread","tags":["countable"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a rope, a cable; a hawser; a cord; a string; a thread; something resembling, likened to, or related to a rope (such as a ray, a beam, a jet, a vein, and so on)","tags":["countable"],"examples":[{"text":"وَلَقَدْ خَلَقْنَا ٱلْإِنسَنَ وَنَعْلَمُ مَا تُوَسْوِسُ بِهِۦ نَفْسُهُۥۖ وَنَحْنُ أَقْرَبُ إِلَيْهِ مِنْ حَبْلِ ٱلْوَرِيدِ","english":"We have created man and know what his spirit suggests to him, and We are closer to him than the rope of his [jugular] vein."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become pregnant; to conceive","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make pregnant, to impregnate","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of حَبِلَ (ḥabila) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"conception"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pregnancy"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *ḥabl-."},"ipa":["/ħabl/","/ħa.bi.la/","/ħab.ba.la/","/ħa.bal/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6974","headword_ar":"حُبْلَى","root":"Hbl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pregnant;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAbilapN","text_ar":"حَابِلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolaAnapN","text_ar":"حَبْلَانَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also occurs in the same sense: (ISd, K) applied to a woman, (S, Mgh,) or, accord. to AZ, to any animal having a nail, (S,) or to any beast, as, for instance, a sheep, or goat, and a cat: (Msb:) pl. of the first"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlaY","text_ar":"حَبَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubolayaAtN","text_ar":"حُبْلَيَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlayaAtN","text_ar":"حَبَالَيَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) which last is pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabaAlaY","text_ar":"حَبَالَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaAbilapN","text_ar":"حَابِلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabalapN","text_ar":"حَبَلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which is extr. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"All~ayolu HubolaY lasota tadoriY","text_ar":"اللَّيْلُ حُبْلَى لَسْتَ تَدْرِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA talidu","text_ar":"مَا تَلِدُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night is pregnant: thou knowest not what it will bring forth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: meaning that the events of the night are not to be trusted. (TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HabolaAnapN","text_ar":"حَبْلَانَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["ISd","K","S","Mgh","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n6975","headword_ar":"حُبْلِىٌّ","root":"Hbl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubolawiY~N","text_ar":"حُبْلَوِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"relating to, one that is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubalaY","text_ar":"حُبَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pregnant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}